{"tid":1258030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【海濱送中】保安局提修例將中環海濱「休憩用地」變解放軍「軍事用地」","createTime":"2019-06-26T01:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T06:49:36.000Z","uid":21873,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7afb759e5ad38885e7c38e0f5c794558b4ed6e0","tid":1258030,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T01:41:58.000Z","msg":"今日將會舉行立法會大會，其中將審議由保安局提交五條的法案，當中有關附屬法例修訂，中環海濱長廊中一段150米長將會變為軍事用地。民主派立法會議員區諾軒將在會上動議「廢除」議案，而朱凱廸議員則動議將附屬法例生效日期押後。<br />\n鑑於條例是「先訂立後審議」方式進行，條例會於6月29日號自動生效，即代表如果6月29日前無法通過二人議案，條例將自動生效。過去《逃犯條例》修訂在兩次逾百萬人遊行下建制派紛紛「跪低」，故團體「保護海濱聯盟」發起聯署，希望得到民意支持，要求全體立法會議員支持「廢除海濱送中」議案。<br />\n<br />\n好似冇人講,係唔係解決左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cabcf129d563a30eb389d52b36c01ed2ef3c779","tid":1258030,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T01:42:24.000Z","msg":"轉至蘋果日報:<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190626/59757221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190626%2F59757221&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=4825e633\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190626%2F59757221&h=bea1ada9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190626/59757221</a>"},{"pid":"b34f5d005529231ebd1a428eff02bd59911f4cec","tid":1258030,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T01:53:14.000Z","msg":"推多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b51ae3d8494495963201ec3790c041b7b136dfb","tid":1258030,"uid":137309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T01:54:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8be11655acbf1b34cd3ab927a6264f5d77d64e4","tid":1258030,"uid":79325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T01